<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #0066cc;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .greeting {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .summary-table {
            border-collapse: collapse;
            width: 100%;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 11px;
        }
        .summary-table th {
            background-color: #0066cc;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        .summary-table td {
            padding: 8px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        .summary-table tr:nth-child(even) {
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
        }
        .summary-table tr:last-child {
            background-color: #e6f2ff;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .summary-table tr:hover {
            background-color: #ddd;
        }
        .note {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 2px solid #0066cc;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .highlight {
            color: #0066cc;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h2>Sample Direct Dispatch to Doctors - ZBM Summary Report</h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <div class="greeting">
            <p>Dear <strong>{{ zbm_name }}</strong>,</p>
            <p>Greetings!</p>
        </div>
        
        <p>Please find below the <span class="highlight">Sample Direct Dispatch Summary Report</span> for your zone as of <strong>{{ current_date }}</strong>.</p>
        
        <p>This report provides a comprehensive overview of all sample requests under your zone, organized by ABM territory:</p>
        
        <div style="margin: 20px 0;">
            {{ summary_table|safe }}
        </div>
        
        <div class="note">
            <strong>ðŸ“Ž Attachment:</strong> A detailed consolidated file containing all request-level data is attached to this email for your reference and further analysis.
        </div>
        
        <p><strong>Key Highlights:</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li>The summary table above shows aggregate metrics for each ABM territory</li>
            <li>The attached consolidated file contains detailed request-level information</li>
            <li>All ABMs under your zone are copied on this email</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p><strong>Report Sections Explained:</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>HO Section:</strong> Requests at Head Office level (cancelled/out of stock + pending at HO)</li>
            <li><strong>HUB Section:</strong> Requests at Hub level (pending invoicing + pending dispatch)</li>
            <li><strong>Delivery Status:</strong> Dispatched and delivered requests</li>
            <li><strong>RTO (Return to Origin):</strong> Breakdown by reason (incomplete address, non-contactable, refused)</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>For any queries or clarifications, please feel free to reach out.</p>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>Best Regards,</strong><br>
            EPD SFA Team<br>
            Abbott</p>
            
            <p style="font-size: 10px; color: #999; margin-top: 20px;">
                <em>This is an auto-generated email. Please do not reply to this email address.</em>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
